---

## 5. Functional Requirements

### 5.1 Application Submission
- Applicants must create a registration application.
- Each application must reference a product.
- Required documents must be uploaded before submission.
- System validates completeness automatically.

### 5.2 Document Management
- Supports PDF, DOCX, XLSX.
- Max file size: 50 MB.
- Version history is maintained.

### 5.3 Review Process
- Applications are assigned to reviewers.
- Reviewers can request clarifications.
- Multiple review rounds are supported.
- All actions are logged.

### 5.4 Decision Management
- Decisions: Approved, Rejected, Deferred
- Justification is mandatory.
- Digital signature required.

### 5.5 Compliance Monitoring
- Incident reports can be submitted by hospitals and manufacturers.
- Risk scoring is calculated automatically.
- Alerts generated for high-risk products.

---

## 6. Business Rules

| Rule ID | Description                                           |
|---------|-------------------------------------------------------|
| BR-01   | Applications require mandatory documents              |
| BR-02   | Only certified reviewers may approve applications     |
| BR-03   | Rejected applications require 3 review notes minimum |
| BR-04   | High-risk incidents reviewed within 48 hours          |
| BR-05   | Products with 3 major incidents are flagged           |

---

