## 11. Example Queries

### Q1: Pending Applications

```sql
SELECT *
FROM applications
WHERE status = 'Under Review';
```

### Q2: Products With Major Incidents

```sql
SELECT p.product_name, COUNT(i.incident_id) AS major_incidents
FROM products p
JOIN incident_reports i
ON p.product_id = i.product_id
WHERE i.severity = 'Major'
GROUP BY p.product_name;
```

### Q3: Reviewer Workload

```sql
SELECT r.name, COUNT(rv.review_id) AS total_reviews
FROM reviewers r
JOIN reviews rv
ON r.reviewer_id = rv.reviewer_id
GROUP BY r.name;
```

---

## 12. Error Handling

| Scenario          | System Behavior  |
|-------------------|------------------|
| Missing documents | Block submission |
| Invalid file      | Reject upload    |
| Review timeout    | Auto-escalation  |
| System failure    | Rollback         |
